        "\n",
        "**Justification:** A hotel guest cannot complete a stay of zero nights. Investigation found approximately 715 zero-night records, of which approximately 680 were marked as NOT canceled. This confirms these are not simply canceled bookings — they are administrative records, same-day processing entries, or data anomalies. Keeping them would distort stay length, occupancy, and revenue calculations.\n"
