        "**Observation:** Groups cancel at 69.5% — nearly seven in ten bookings never complete. Offline TA/TO and Online TA cancel at 43.3% and 37.5% respectively, both above the hotel average of 41.1%. Direct bookings cancel at only 17.4%.\n",
